igotu2gpx (0.2.93-0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Released the third release candidate of igotu2gpx 0.3.0.
  * Changes since version 0.2.92:
    - Updates fixed by supplying the missing Host: header
    - Include lib32 and lib64 in plugin search
    - Option to group points into segments instead of tracks on GPX output added, manpage updates
    - Debian packaging fix on Hardy
    - Support to recognize a GT-200e
    - Do not crash if no connection plugins are found

 -- Michael Hofmann <mh21@piware.de>  Sun, 04 Oct 2009 15:39:15 +0200

